com.unvired.chyme.api

Class Chart

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unvired.chyme.api.Chart

  • public class Chart
extends java.lang.Object
    The Chart class provides an abstraction to represent tabular data graphically.

    A chart has the following components.

    • Chart Type - indicates the type of Chart to be plotted. The currently supported types are BAR, COLUMN, LINE and PIE.
    • Description or Title - Provides a brief description of the data being represented
    • Categories - Represents the first dimension of tabular data in a chart
    • Series - Represents the second dimension of tabular data in a chart
    Author:
    Unvired Inc
